headline: Principal to Announce Second Quarter 2025 Financial Results
summary: DES MOINES, Iowa, July 01, 2025--Principal Financial Group® (Nasdaq: PFG) announced today that it will release second quarter 2025 financial results after U.S. markets close on Monday, July 28, 2025.

headline: Principal® Employees Surpass 145,000 Volunteer Hours in Celebration of the Company’s 145th Anniversary
summary: DES MOINES, Iowa, July 01, 2025--Principal Financial Group® today announced the successful completion of its 145,000-hour global volunteerism goal, a milestone set in July of 2024 to celebrate the company’s 145th anniversary and enduring commitment to building strong communities.
